<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/remploy-pension-scheme-trustees-ltd> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Remploy Pension Scheme Trustees Ltd is the trustee for the Remploy Ltd Pension and Assurance Scheme, the pension scheme for employees of the Disabled Persons’ Employment Corporation Ltd (previously known as Remploy Ltd) prior to 4 June 2015. Remploy Pension Scheme Trustees Ltd is a private company limited by guarantee without share capital and incorporated in 2011. The Department for work and Pensions is the principal employer for the pension scheme. Remploy Pension Scheme Trustees Ltd works with the Department for Work and Pensions ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
